cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

This paper is primarily focused on image segmentation using a combination of deep learning and active contour models. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also introduces a novel framework that involves training a convolutional neural network (CNN) and an active contour model (ACM) together, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG and cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with aerial images, which could fall under the category of computer graphics (cs.GR) or multimedia (cs.MM).
